@${F^{\times} = F - \{0\}} is a multiplicative group (since @${0} doesn't have a multiplicative inverse)

Order is @${p^n - 1 \rightarrow \forall \in F^{\times}, a^{p^n - 1} = 1 \Rightarrow a^p^n = a \rightarrow a^p^n - a = 0}
